{#
/**
 * @file
 * Template for US Government Power Analysis page.
 *
 * Available variables:
 * - title: Page title
 * - intro: Introduction content with lead and paragraphs
 * - branches: Government branches with entities and power profiles
 */
#}

<div class="container py-4">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-11 mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-center mb-3 text-cyan">{{ title }}</h1>
      
      <div class="lead mb-4 text-muted-light text-center">
        {{ intro.lead }}
      </div>
      
      <div class="text-center mb-4">
        <a href="/agent-power-framework" class="btn btn-outline-primary me-2">
          <i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i> Back to Framework
        </a>
        <a href="/agent-power-framework/evaluations" class="btn btn-outline-cyan me-2">
          <i class="fas fa-list"></i> View All Evaluations
        </a>
        <a href="/agent-power-framework" class="btn btn-outline-success">
          <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i> Example Assessment
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="alert alert-info-cyan mb-4">
        {% for paragraph in intro.paragraphs %}
          <p{% if loop.last %} class="mb-0"{% endif %}>{{ paragraph }}</p>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
      
      <h2 class="mt-5 mb-3 text-cyan">
        <i class="fas fa-chart-bar me-2"></i>Military Ranks: Framework Evaluation Results
      </h2>
      
      {# Umbrella Controls #}
      <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-3">
        <div>
          <button class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-cyan me-2" id="expandAllCards">
            <i class="fas fa-expand-alt me-1"></i>Expand All Cards
          </button>
          <button class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-cyan" id="collapseAllCards">
            <i class="fas fa-compress-alt me-1"></i>Collapse All Cards
          </button>
        </div>
        <div>
          <button class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-info me-2" id="expandAllSubDims">
            <i class="fas fa-list-ul me-1"></i>Expand All Sub-Dimensions
          </button>
          <button class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-info" id="collapseAllSubDims">
            <i class="fas fa-minus-square me-1"></i>Collapse All Sub-Dimensions
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="alert alert-success mb-4">
        <p class="mb-2">
          <strong><i class="fas fa-check-circle me-2"></i>Evaluation Complete:</strong> All 29 military ranks have been assessed against the Agent Power Framework's 30 sub-dimensions (6 per core dimension).
        </p>
        <p class="mb-0">
          <strong>Key Finding:</strong> Sub-dimension analysis reveals nuanced power profiles - warrant officers show asymmetric capabilities (high synthesis scores of 5-7, but authority scores of 2-4), while senior NCOs score exceptionally high on trust networks (6) despite moderate overall authority (4).
        </p>
      </div>
      
      {# Evaluated Ranks Display with Collapsible Cards and 30 Sub-Dimensions #}
      <div class="accordion accordion-forseti" id="ranksAccordion">
      {% for rank in branches %}
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <h2 class="accordion-header" id="heading-{{ loop.index }}">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse-card-{{ loop.index }}" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse-card-{{ loop.index }}" aria-labelledby="heading-{{ loop.index }}">
              <div class="d-flex align-items-center w-100" style="pointer-events: none;">
                <div class="badge bg-{% if rank.level_avg >= 8 %}success{% elseif rank.level_avg >= 6 %}info{% elseif rank.level_avg >= 4 %}warning{% else %}secondary{% endif %} fs-5 p-2 me-3" style="min-width: 60px;">
                  {{ rank.level_avg }}
                </div>
                <div class="flex-grow-1">
                  <h5 class="text-cyan mb-0">{{ rank.position }}</h5>
                  <div class="text-info small">{{ rank.title }}</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </button>
          </h2>
          <div id="collapse-card-{{ loop.index }}" class="accordion-collapse collapse rank-collapse" aria-labelledby="heading-{{ loop.index }}">
            <div class="accordion-body p-4">
              
              {# Rank Details #}
              <div class="mb-3">
                <div class="text-muted-light small">
                  <span class="badge bg-dark me-2">{{ rank.rank_type }}</span>
                  <i class="fas fa-users me-1"></i>{{ rank.scope }}
                </div>
              </div>
            
            {# Main 5 Dimensions Summary #}
            <div class="row g-2 mb-3">
              <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="p-2 rounded" style="background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1);">
                  <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                    <span class="small text-cyan"><i class="fas fa-database me-1"></i>Info Access</span>
                    <span class="badge bg-{% if rank.power_profile.info >= 8 %}success{% elseif rank.power_profile.info >= 6 %}info{% elseif rank.power_profile.info >= 4 %}warning{% else %}secondary{% endif %}">
                      {{ rank.power_profile.info }}/9
                    </span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="p-2 rounded" style="background: rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.1);">
                  <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                    <span class="small text-success"><i class="fas fa-coins me-1"></i>Resources</span>
                    <span class="badge bg-{% if rank.power_profile.resource >= 8 %}success{% elseif rank.power_profile.resource >= 6 %}info{% elseif rank.power_profile.resource >= 4 %}warning{% else %}secondary{% endif %}">
                      {{ rank.power_profile.resource }}/9
                    </span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="p-2 rounded" style="background: rgba(233, 30, 99, 0.1);">
                  <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                    <span class="small text-danger"><i class="fas fa-gavel me-1"></i>Authority</span>
                    <span class="badge bg-{% if rank.power_profile.authority >= 8 %}success{% elseif rank.power_profile.authority >= 6 %}info{% elseif rank.power_profile.authority >= 4 %}warning{% else %}secondary{% endif %}">
                      {{ rank.power_profile.authority }}/9
                    </span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="p-2 rounded" style="background: rgba(156, 39, 176, 0.1);">
                  <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                    <span class="small text-purple"><i class="fas fa-project-diagram me-1"></i>Network</span>
                    <span class="badge bg-{% if rank.power_profile.network >= 8 %}success{% elseif rank.power_profile.network >= 6 %}info{% elseif rank.power_profile.network >= 4 %}warning{% else %}secondary{% endif %}">
                      {{ rank.power_profile.network }}/9
                    </span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="p-2 rounded" style="background: rgba(255, 235, 59, 0.1);">
                  <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
                    <span class="small text-warning"><i class="fas fa-brain me-1"></i>Synthesis</span>
                    <span class="badge bg-{% if rank.power_profile.synthesis >= 8 %}success{% elseif rank.power_profile.synthesis >= 6 %}info{% elseif rank.power_profile.synthesis >= 4 %}warning{% else %}secondary{% endif %}">
                      {{ rank.power_profile.synthesis }}/9
                    </span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            {# Expandable 30 Sub-Dimensions Detail #}
            <div class="accordion accordion-forseti mt-3" id="subdim-{{ loop.index }}">
              <div class="accordion-item">
                <h2 class="accordion-header" id="subdim-heading-{{ loop.index }}">
                  <button class="accordion-button collapsed subdim-collapse" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse-subdim-{{ loop.index }}" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse-subdim-{{ loop.index }}" aria-labelledby="subdim-heading-{{ loop.index }}">
                    <i class="fas fa-list-ul me-2"></i>View 30 Sub-Dimensions Breakdown
                  </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="collapse-subdim-{{ loop.index }}" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="subdim-heading-{{ loop.index }}">
                  <div class="accordion-body">
                    
                    {# Information Access (6 sub-dimensions) #}
                    <div class="mb-3">
                      <h6 class="text-cyan mb-2"><i class="fas fa-database me-2"></i>Information Access</h6>
                      <div class="row g-2 small">
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                          <div class="d-flex justify-content-between p-1">
                            <span>Scope & Scale</span>
                            <span class="badge bg-{% if rank.sub_dimensions.info_scope >= 8 %}success{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.info_scope >= 6 %}info{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.info_scope >= 4 %}warning{% else %}secondary{% endif %} rounded-pill">{{ rank.sub_dimensions.info_scope }}</span>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                          <div class="d-flex justify-content-between p-1">
                            <span>Restrictions</span>
                            <span class="badge bg-{% if rank.sub_dimensions.info_restrictions >= 8 %}success{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.info_restrictions >= 6 %}info{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.info_restrictions >= 4 %}warning{% else %}secondary{% endif %} rounded-pill">{{ rank.sub_dimensions.info_restrictions }}</span>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                          <div class="d-flex justify-content-between p-1">
                            <span>Classification</span>
                            <span class="badge bg-{% if rank.sub_dimensions.info_classification >= 8 %}success{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.info_classification >= 6 %}info{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.info_classification >= 4 %}warning{% else %}secondary{% endif %} rounded-pill">{{ rank.sub_dimensions.info_classification }}</span>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                          <div class="d-flex justify-content-between p-1">
                            <span>Temporal Reach</span>
                            <span class="badge bg-{% if rank.sub_dimensions.info_temporal >= 8 %}success{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.info_temporal >= 6 %}info{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.info_temporal >= 4 %}warning{% else %}secondary{% endif %} rounded-pill">{{ rank.sub_dimensions.info_temporal }}</span>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                          <div class="d-flex justify-content-between p-1">
                            <span>Source Diversity</span>
                            <span class="badge bg-{% if rank.sub_dimensions.info_source_diversity >= 8 %}success{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.info_source_diversity >= 6 %}info{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.info_source_diversity >= 4 %}warning{% else %}secondary{% endif %} rounded-pill">{{ rank.sub_dimensions.info_source_diversity }}</span>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                          <div class="d-flex justify-content-between p-1">
                            <span>Detail & Verification</span>
                            <span class="badge bg-{% if rank.sub_dimensions.info_detail >= 8 %}success{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.info_detail >= 6 %}info{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.info_detail >= 4 %}warning{% else %}secondary{% endif %} rounded-pill">{{ rank.sub_dimensions.info_detail }}</span>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    {# Resource Control (6 sub-dimensions) #}
                    <div class="mb-3">
                      <h6 class="text-success mb-2"><i class="fas fa-coins me-2"></i>Resource Control</h6>
                      <div class="row g-2 small">
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                          <div class="d-flex justify-content-between p-1">
                            <span>Computational</span>
                            <span class="badge bg-{% if rank.sub_dimensions.resource_computational >= 8 %}success{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.resource_computational >= 6 %}info{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.resource_computational >= 4 %}warning{% else %}secondary{% endif %} rounded-pill">{{ rank.sub_dimensions.resource_computational }}</span>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                          <div class="d-flex justify-content-between p-1">
                            <span>Financial</span>
                            <span class="badge bg-{% if rank.sub_dimensions.resource_financial >= 8 %}success{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.resource_financial >= 6 %}info{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.resource_financial >= 4 %}warning{% else %}secondary{% endif %} rounded-pill">{{ rank.sub_dimensions.resource_financial }}</span>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                          <div class="d-flex justify-content-between p-1">
                            <span>Infrastructure</span>
                            <span class="badge bg-{% if rank.sub_dimensions.resource_infrastructure >= 8 %}success{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.resource_infrastructure >= 6 %}info{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.resource_infrastructure >= 4 %}warning{% else %}secondary{% endif %} rounded-pill">{{ rank.sub_dimensions.resource_infrastructure }}</span>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                          <div class="d-flex justify-content-between p-1">
                            <span>Human Capital</span>
                            <span class="badge bg-{% if rank.sub_dimensions.resource_human >= 8 %}success{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.resource_human >= 6 %}info{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.resource_human >= 4 %}warning{% else %}secondary{% endif %} rounded-pill">{{ rank.sub_dimensions.resource_human }}</span>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                          <div class="d-flex justify-content-between p-1">
                            <span>Energy</span>
                            <span class="badge bg-{% if rank.sub_dimensions.resource_energy >= 8 %}success{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.resource_energy >= 6 %}info{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.resource_energy >= 4 %}warning{% else %}secondary{% endif %} rounded-pill">{{ rank.sub_dimensions.resource_energy }}</span>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                          <div class="d-flex justify-content-between p-1">
                            <span>Time & Attention</span>
                            <span class="badge bg-{% if rank.sub_dimensions.resource_time >= 8 %}success{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.resource_time >= 6 %}info{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.resource_time >= 4 %}warning{% else %}secondary{% endif %} rounded-pill">{{ rank.sub_dimensions.resource_time }}</span>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    {# Authority & Permission (6 sub-dimensions) #}
                    <div class="mb-3">
                      <h6 class="text-danger mb-2"><i class="fas fa-gavel me-2"></i>Authority & Permission</h6>
                      <div class="row g-2 small">
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                          <div class="d-flex justify-content-between p-1">
                            <span>Legal Authorization</span>
                            <span class="badge bg-{% if rank.sub_dimensions.authority_legal >= 8 %}success{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.authority_legal >= 6 %}info{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.authority_legal >= 4 %}warning{% else %}secondary{% endif %} rounded-pill">{{ rank.sub_dimensions.authority_legal }}</span>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                          <div class="d-flex justify-content-between p-1">
                            <span>Jurisdictional Reach</span>
                            <span class="badge bg-{% if rank.sub_dimensions.authority_jurisdiction >= 8 %}success{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.authority_jurisdiction >= 6 %}info{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.authority_jurisdiction >= 4 %}warning{% else %}secondary{% endif %} rounded-pill">{{ rank.sub_dimensions.authority_jurisdiction }}</span>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                          <div class="d-flex justify-content-between p-1">
                            <span>Hierarchical Position</span>
                            <span class="badge bg-{% if rank.sub_dimensions.authority_hierarchy >= 8 %}success{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.authority_hierarchy >= 6 %}info{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.authority_hierarchy >= 4 %}warning{% else %}secondary{% endif %} rounded-pill">{{ rank.sub_dimensions.authority_hierarchy }}</span>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                          <div class="d-flex justify-content-between p-1">
                            <span>Financial Authority</span>
                            <span class="badge bg-{% if rank.sub_dimensions.authority_financial >= 8 %}success{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.authority_financial >= 6 %}info{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.authority_financial >= 4 %}warning{% else %}secondary{% endif %} rounded-pill">{{ rank.sub_dimensions.authority_financial }}</span>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                          <div class="d-flex justify-content-between p-1">
                            <span>Territorial Control</span>
                            <span class="badge bg-{% if rank.sub_dimensions.authority_territory >= 8 %}success{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.authority_territory >= 6 %}info{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.authority_territory >= 4 %}warning{% else %}secondary{% endif %} rounded-pill">{{ rank.sub_dimensions.authority_territory }}</span>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                          <div class="d-flex justify-content-between p-1">
                            <span>Legitimacy & Trust</span>
                            <span class="badge bg-{% if rank.sub_dimensions.authority_legitimacy >= 8 %}success{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.authority_legitimacy >= 6 %}info{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.authority_legitimacy >= 4 %}warning{% else %}secondary{% endif %} rounded-pill">{{ rank.sub_dimensions.authority_legitimacy }}</span>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    {# Network Position (6 sub-dimensions) #}
                    <div class="mb-3">
                      <h6 class="text-purple mb-2"><i class="fas fa-project-diagram me-2"></i>Network Position</h6>
                      <div class="row g-2 small">
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                          <div class="d-flex justify-content-between p-1">
                            <span>Trust Networks</span>
                            <span class="badge bg-{% if rank.sub_dimensions.network_trust >= 8 %}success{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.network_trust >= 6 %}info{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.network_trust >= 4 %}warning{% else %}secondary{% endif %} rounded-pill">{{ rank.sub_dimensions.network_trust }}</span>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                          <div class="d-flex justify-content-between p-1">
                            <span>Dependencies</span>
                            <span class="badge bg-{% if rank.sub_dimensions.network_dependencies >= 8 %}success{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.network_dependencies >= 6 %}info{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.network_dependencies >= 4 %}warning{% else %}secondary{% endif %} rounded-pill">{{ rank.sub_dimensions.network_dependencies }}</span>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                          <div class="d-flex justify-content-between p-1">
                            <span>Gatekeeping</span>
                            <span class="badge bg-{% if rank.sub_dimensions.network_gatekeeping >= 8 %}success{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.network_gatekeeping >= 6 %}info{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.network_gatekeeping >= 4 %}warning{% else %}secondary{% endif %} rounded-pill">{{ rank.sub_dimensions.network_gatekeeping }}</span>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                          <div class="d-flex justify-content-between p-1">
                            <span>Influence Reach</span>
                            <span class="badge bg-{% if rank.sub_dimensions.network_influence >= 8 %}success{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.network_influence >= 6 %}info{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.network_influence >= 4 %}warning{% else %}secondary{% endif %} rounded-pill">{{ rank.sub_dimensions.network_influence }}</span>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                          <div class="d-flex justify-content-between p-1">
                            <span>Reputation Capital</span>
                            <span class="badge bg-{% if rank.sub_dimensions.network_reputation >= 8 %}success{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.network_reputation >= 6 %}info{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.network_reputation >= 4 %}warning{% else %}secondary{% endif %} rounded-pill">{{ rank.sub_dimensions.network_reputation }}</span>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                          <div class="d-flex justify-content-between p-1">
                            <span>Mobilization</span>
                            <span class="badge bg-{% if rank.sub_dimensions.network_mobilization >= 8 %}success{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.network_mobilization >= 6 %}info{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.network_mobilization >= 4 %}warning{% else %}secondary{% endif %} rounded-pill">{{ rank.sub_dimensions.network_mobilization }}</span>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    {# Synthesis & Application (6 sub-dimensions) #}
                    <div class="mb-0">
                      <h6 class="text-warning mb-2"><i class="fas fa-brain me-2"></i>Synthesis & Application</h6>
                      <div class="row g-2 small">
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                          <div class="d-flex justify-content-between p-1">
                            <span>Pattern Recognition</span>
                            <span class="badge bg-{% if rank.sub_dimensions.synthesis_pattern >= 8 %}success{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.synthesis_pattern >= 6 %}info{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.synthesis_pattern >= 4 %}warning{% else %}secondary{% endif %} rounded-pill">{{ rank.sub_dimensions.synthesis_pattern }}</span>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                          <div class="d-flex justify-content-between p-1">
                            <span>Creative Ideation</span>
                            <span class="badge bg-{% if rank.sub_dimensions.synthesis_creativity >= 8 %}success{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.synthesis_creativity >= 6 %}info{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.synthesis_creativity >= 4 %}warning{% else %}secondary{% endif %} rounded-pill">{{ rank.sub_dimensions.synthesis_creativity }}</span>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                          <div class="d-flex justify-content-between p-1">
                            <span>Strategic Planning</span>
                            <span class="badge bg-{% if rank.sub_dimensions.synthesis_planning >= 8 %}success{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.synthesis_planning >= 6 %}info{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.synthesis_planning >= 4 %}warning{% else %}secondary{% endif %} rounded-pill">{{ rank.sub_dimensions.synthesis_planning }}</span>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                          <div class="d-flex justify-content-between p-1">
                            <span>Decision Quality</span>
                            <span class="badge bg-{% if rank.sub_dimensions.synthesis_decision >= 8 %}success{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.synthesis_decision >= 6 %}info{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.synthesis_decision >= 4 %}warning{% else %}secondary{% endif %} rounded-pill">{{ rank.sub_dimensions.synthesis_decision }}</span>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                          <div class="d-flex justify-content-between p-1">
                            <span>Learning Capability</span>
                            <span class="badge bg-{% if rank.sub_dimensions.synthesis_learning >= 8 %}success{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.synthesis_learning >= 6 %}info{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.synthesis_learning >= 4 %}warning{% else %}secondary{% endif %} rounded-pill">{{ rank.sub_dimensions.synthesis_learning }}</span>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                          <div class="d-flex justify-content-between p-1">
                            <span>Memory & Recall</span>
                            <span class="badge bg-{% if rank.sub_dimensions.synthesis_memory >= 8 %}success{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.synthesis_memory >= 6 %}info{% elseif rank.sub_dimensions.synthesis_memory >= 4 %}warning{% else %}secondary{% endif %} rounded-pill">{{ rank.sub_dimensions.synthesis_memory }}</span>
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      {% endfor %}
      </div>{# End ranksAccordion #}
      
      <div class="alert alert-warning mt-5">
        <h5 class="text-warning mb-3">
          <i class="fas fa-chart-line me-2"></i>Framework Evaluation Insights
        </h5>
        <p class="mb-2">
          <strong>Power Level Distribution:</strong>
        </p>
        <ul class="mb-2">
          <li><strong>Level 8-9 (Cross-Institutional to Approaching Omniscient):</strong> President (8.8), Secretary of Defense (8.2)</li>
          <li><strong>Level 7 (Multi-Domain Academic):</strong> Four-Star Generals (7.0-7.6), Three-Star Generals (7.0)</li>
          <li><strong>Level 6 (Domain-Specific Professional):</strong> Two-Star and One-Star Generals (6.0)</li>
          <li><strong>Level 5 (Specialized):</strong> Colonels and Lt Colonels (5.0)</li>
          <li><strong>Level 4 (Tactical/Operational):</strong> Majors, Captains, Senior NCOs (4.0-4.8)</li>
          <li><strong>Level 3 (Personal/Commercial):</strong> Lieutenants, Mid-level NCOs (3.0-3.4)</li>
